snippet.title: Carnival Hunt Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Follow and support us on Kickstarter to make this game real.
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/...

Carnival Hunt is a horror, first-person asymmetric social multiplayer game. One player takes on the role of the Carnival Monster, and the other players play as Bunnies. Each side is struggling to survive. Not only do the bunnies need a charge to survive, so does the monster. No two playthroughs are ever the same.

Add to your Steam wishlist and get notified when it becomes available. 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/11...

Follow us on Twitter, LinkedIn, Facebook and Instagram for studio news and involve with our community of developers and fans.
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/beernightst...
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BeerNightStudio
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Beernightstu...
Linkedin: https://www.linkedin.com/company/beer...
